            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_12gc' title='Col. 12GC &mdash; HL Deb 04 March 1996 vol 570 c12GC' name='column_12gc' href='#column_12gc' rel='bookmark'>12GC</a>
            <q>it is essential that we should not attempt to lay down detailed rules or formulae. Rather, it is surely best to confer general powers on a body so constituted as to command the confidence of all the interests concerned".&#x2014;[<span class="italic">Official Report,</span> 18/11/58; col. 562.]</q>
