          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0570P0-01154'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960304_GCR_144' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        5.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0570P0-01155'>
        <a name='S5LV0570P0_19960304_GCR_145'>  </a>
