          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0570P0-01160'>
        <a name='S5LV0570P0_19960304_GCR_150'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-simon-arthur' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0570P0_19960304_GCR_150' title='Link to this speech by Mr Simon Arthur' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-simon-arthur" title="Mr Simon Arthur">Lord Glenarthur</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            With that assurance, I am very grateful to my noble friend and beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
